Why alchemy wouldn't help create some combine?<br />
<br />
<br />
Have a look at cultural recipes for barbarians for exemple.<br />
Barbs don't have any forager class, but still many cultural requires foraged stuff.<br />
why not a potion as an alternate component for some foraged items?<br />
<br />
<br />
And i really like the idea of foraging shamans too (and it would fix the problem for cultural recipes needing foraged stuff btw).<br />
